OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThe morning will begin cloudy
OL,6,Fbut dry, outbreaks of rain soon spread
OL,7,Feast becoming heavy at times over the
OL,8,Fhills. This rain will clear briefly
OL,9,Faround midday with further rain
OL,10,Fpushing east in the afternoon.
OL,11,FFreshening southerly winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FThe night will continue
OL,14,Fcloudy and mild with further outbreaks
OL,15,Fof rain, this heavy at times
OL,16,Fparticularly over the hills.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
