OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FEarly rain will clear east as
OL,6,Fthe wind falls light in the morning.
OL,7,FSunny spells will increase before
OL,8,Fshowers spread southeast from late
OL,9,Fafternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,12,FTuesday and Wednesday begin frosty but
OL,13,Fstay dry and sunny. The wind will
OL,14,Fstrengthen on Thursday when outbreaks
OL,15,Fof rain spread east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
